---
<Layout active="process" title="How work flows · Beadhive" description="The Beadhive mental model in one breath and the full planning → dispatch → develop → review → merge pipeline, with its spike, bounce, and replan loops.">
<div class="pagegrid">
  <nav class="toc" aria-label="On this page">
    <p class="toc-title">On this page</p>
    <a class="head" href="#how">The mental model</a>
    <a class="sub" href="#how-tenets">The tenets</a>
